{"tid":358933,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"老婦橫過宜安街 遭紅Van撞倒捲車底","createTime":"2017-08-14T05:29:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-14T13:09:06.000Z","uid":19552,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d4b4fbc674b85f9a47337d1aab5b052ec21a5f7f","tid":358933,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T05:29:08.000Z","msg":"中午12時半，一輛小巴剛駛離牛頭角宜安街站頭後不久，至通明街附近撞倒一名橫過馬路的老婦，並將她捲入車底，消防接報到場將老婦救出，再送院搶救。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170814/large/1502687775_f93e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170814%2Flarge%2F1502687775_f93e.jpg&h=824a6ca3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"723ee1c9546bbd1529a8e966e18c19d1e6ff8e00","tid":358933,"uid":50740,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T05:35:23.000Z","msg":"福氣"},{"pid":"92f1c30e6ec2621bb0d2c790e4c0df0839faaf08","tid":358933,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T05:43:57.000Z","msg":"廢老"},{"pid":"733324b4b683ffdbcd85f043346e638af27e291f","tid":358933,"uid":2772,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T05:46:19.000Z","msg":"你估牛頭到先定馬面到先"},{"pid":"33923637ff9dc9199913e381dd98eebeb7aa1fa5","tid":358933,"uid":122,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T07:07:45.000Z","msg":"觀塘發生交通意外，中午12時31分，一輛由觀塘開往荃灣的公共小巴，在宜安街站頭開出時，將一名橫過馬路的老婦捲入車底，老婦下半身摺曲，不能動彈，消防員接報到場，將老婦救出，送院搶救，警方正調查意外原因。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">有目擊者表示，當時見老婦行出馬路時，曾大聲提醒她：「有車嚟，唔好行出去」，但說時遲，老婦已遭小巴撞及。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n受意外影響，宜安街往康寧道方向近通明街的部分行車線現已封閉，交通受阻。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170814/photo/bkn-20170814124106363-0814_00822_001_01p.jpg?20170814142024\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170814%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170814124106363-0814_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20170814142024&h=2423be69&s={SIZE}\" />"}